    <div class="marquee animated animatedFadeInUp fadeInUp">
        <p style="color: black;"> <strong>PLEASE NOTE:</strong> Don't go out much only one person from each family should take responsibility to go out and bring household materials <strong>||</strong> 
            The person who goes out should wear a full arm shirt and shoes <strong>||</strong> 
            As soon as you enter home please keep your shoes outside don't wear the same inside the house. Immediately change your dress don't sit any where wearing the same dress. Take bath preferably head bath with soap. <strong>||</strong> 
            People more than 60 - diabetic, heart or kidney disease patient should not go out. <strong>|</strong> 
            Wash hand frequently with water and soap. <strong>||</strong> 
            Don't touch your eyes nose with hands. <strong>||</strong> 
            Wash all packed good items and vegetables thoroughly with water. <strong>|</strong> 
            Don't gather much people in a room. <strong>||</strong> 
            Keep distance from elderly. <strong>||</strong> 
            Don't play outdoor games. <strong>||</strong> 
            Don't play games involving more than 3 to 4 people at a time. <strong>||</strong> 
            If anybody has fever cough then he or she should stay away from others. <strong>||</strong> 
            Don't allow maids to come. <strong>||</strong> 
            Eat healthy food avoid fried and junk foods bcoz you if you get I'll then need to go to doctor and going to doctor at this time chance of infection very high as doctor comes with contact with many others. <strong>||</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
<script>
     var ctx = document.getElementById('myChart').getContext('2d');
     var chart = new Chart(ctx, {
        type: 'line',
        data: {
            labels: <%- JSON.stringify(labels); %>,
            datasets: [{
                label: 'Total Cases of Corona',
                backgroundColor:"red",
                borderColor:"white",
                data: <%- JSON.stringify(data); %>,
            }]
        },
